OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FThe Princess of Wales is embarking on
OL,7,Fa new "global mission" on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fas she makes her first overseas royal
OL,9,Ftrip since her cancer diagnosis.
OL,11,FKate will step off the plane and get
OL,12,Fto work in the Emilia-Romagna region
OL,13,Fof Italy in what is being described as
OL,14,Fa "huge moment" for the princess
OL,15,Fpersonally.
OL,17,FThe future queen has not been on an
OL,18,Finternational work trip since 2022,
OL,19,Fand senior members of her team said
OL,20,Fthat she is now "taking it up a gear"
OL,21,Fon this important Italian visit.
OL,26,@oD@VO]vD@COUvD@OO]|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
