FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FShe will visit the town of Reggio
OL,7,FEmilia, which has pioneered an
OL,8,Fapproach to early childhood which is
OL,9,Frecognised around the world.
OL,11,FThe princess was diagnosed with cancer
OL,12,Fin 2024, and much of her work went on
OL,13,Fhold during that time.
OL,15,FCourtiers at Kensington Palace have
OL,16,Fbeen trying to balance her work and
OL,17,Fher recovery since her chemotherapy
OL,18,Ffinished.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FGiven the volume of chemotherapy Kate
OL,7,Fhad during her treatment and the toll
OL,8,Fit's taken on her body, this visit
OL,9,Fmarks "an important step in her
OL,10,Fjourney", a source added.
OL,12,FThey said: "She takes great joy from
OL,13,Fthis work. I think it is only right
OL,14,Fthat her first international trip
OL,15,Fsince her illness is one that is
OL,16,Ffocused on an issue that she is
OL,17,Fcommitted to championing for decades
OL,18,Fto come, and is a real issue that she
OL,19,Fwants to shine a spotlight on."
OL,26,@rD@HO]{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
