CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FKate is trying to link up her 15-year
OL,7,Fprogramme of work on early years
OL,8,Fchildhood development with other
OL,9,Finternational approaches, which is why
OL,10,Fshe picked this location near Bologna
OL,11,Fin northern Italy.
OL,13,FThe "Reggio Emilia Approach" was
OL,14,Fdeveloped after the Second World War
OL,15,Fand has transformed the life chances
OL,16,Fof generations of children, according
OL,17,Fto experts in this field.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FIt focuses on children from birth to
OL,7,Fsix years old, and focuses on shaping
OL,8,Fthe future health and well-being of
OL,9,Feach child as they develop into
OL,10,Fadulthood.
OL,12,FThe Italian example aligns with the
OL,13,Fwork the princess does in the UK with
OL,14,Fthe Royal Foundation's Centre for
OL,15,FEarly Childhood, and the issue has
OL,16,Fbecome her "life's work", say royal
OL,17,Faides.
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FThe Centre's CEO, Christian Guy, who
OL,7,Fis with Kate in Italy, said: "From
OL,8,Fpregnancy to the age of five,
OL,9,Fchildren's brains are developing at an
OL,10,Fextraordinary rate, forming the
OL,11,Fconnections that will underpin how
OL,12,Fthey think, feel, relate to others and
OL,13,Fnavigate the world for the rest of
OL,14,Ftheir lives."
OL,16,FMr Guy told British and Italian
OL,17,Freporters gathered in Italy that the
OL,18,Fprincess intends to elevate the early
OL,19,Fyears issue to give it the same
OL,20,F"urgency as climate change".
OL,26,@vD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,F"A child's brain," he said, "forms
OL,7,Fmore than one million connections
OL,8,Fevery second", and it "reaches 90% of
OL,9,Fits adult size by age five."
OL,11,FThe pre-schools in Reggio Emilia focus
OL,12,Fon learning through relationships and
OL,13,Fusing the environment around them as
OL,14,Fthe "third teacher".
OL,16,FThe role of nature, in particular, in
OL,17,Fall our lives is something that Kate
OL,18,Funderstands more fully following the
OL,19,Flife-changing event that the cancer
OL,20,Fjourney was for her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@RO]vD@EOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
