PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FIt's understood that the last few
OL,7,Fyears have been a grounding experience
OL,8,Fand given the princess a new
OL,9,Fperspective on all aspects of life.
OL,11,FKate intends to take the learnings
OL,12,Ffrom this corner of Italy back to the
OL,13,FUK.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
