PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FThis is her first official royal visit
OL,7,Fto the country, although palace
OL,8,Fsources said the princess had been
OL,9,F"remembering the happy memories that
OL,10,Fshe had during her time in Florence on
OL,11,Fher gap year".
OL,13,FThey said: "She's had many
OL,14,Fconversations with her husband, the
OL,15,FPrince of Wales, and her children
OL,16,Fabout this trip, and they're looking
OL,17,Fforward to hearing about it".
OL,26,@sD@MO]uD@LOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,F"Undoubtedly, this is a huge moment
OL,7,Ffor the princess", said an aide when
OL,8,Fasked about what the visit means to
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,F"Although there will be many
OL,12,Fhighlights of 2026, I think this being
OL,13,Fher first official international
OL,14,Fvisit, post her recovery, I think this
OL,15,Fis a really significant moment for
OL,16,Fher."
OL,26,@oD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
