PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778731463
OL,3,CKate's solo journey to Italy marks her
OL,4,Creturn to overseas travel after cancer
OL,6,FIt's understood Kate wants to draw on
OL,7,Fthe expertise in early years in other
OL,8,Fparts of the world, and her staff said
OL,9,Fshe was now on a "global mission"
OL,10,Fwhich would inevitably mean further
OL,11,Ftravel to deepen her understanding.
OL,13,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,14,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,15,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,16,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
